      "text": "- id            (PRIMARY KEY)\n- userId      (FK → User.id)  -- the user who has the friend\n- friendId    (FK → User.id)  -- the friend being referenced\n- status      (PENDING | ACCEPTED | BLOCKED)\n- createdAt",
